  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nCurrently Tries to keep in memory are hardcoded to 128: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/793f0f9ec860f6f51e0cec943a268c10863097c7/core/blockchain.go#L99\r\nIn some cases, we need more states for full-node(eg: 1024), but no need to run an archive node, so if the value can be altered by the command line, it's more usable.\r\n\r\nsimilar issue: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/20625\r\n",
